# {{PROJECT_NAME}}

## Role: Project Orchestrator

This directory is managed by the Project Orchestrator. Code is never modified directly here. The `orchestrator/` package delegates work to Workspace Orchestrators (WOs) that run inside each workspace.

## Hierarchy

```
orchestrator/
├── PO: routing + execution plan (phases + dependencies)
├── Executor: parallel/sequential WO execution
├── Each workspace/ (runtime guidance auto-loaded per runtime)
└── ARCHIVE/ → credentials & configs (never modify)
```

## What the Orchestrator Does

- **Route** user requests to the correct workspace
- **Analyze** workspace dependencies dynamically to create execution phases
- **Execute** WOs in parallel/sequential order using the configured runtime
- **Log** results to `.tasks/`
- **Notify** results back to the requesting channel
- **Never** modify code directly — always delegates to workspaces
